Description:
   Cloak:oathbreaker is the Warlock's signature remort cloak. It shrouds the
   caster in dark, oath-defying energy that grants a chance to completely
   avoid incoming magical (spell) damage.

   When the caster would take non-physical damage that does not have
   NO_REFLECT or NO_ABSORB flags, there is a pseudo_level / 10 percent chance
   that the cloak shatters the incoming magic harmlessly. For example, at
   pseudo-level 100, there is a 10% chance to avoid each spell hit entirely.

   The cloak does not protect against physical damage. For physical avoidance,
   see cloak:transcendence (Assassin).

   Duration scales with pseudo-level (pseudo_level / 8 rounds).
